query: SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS movie_company, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(t.title) AS complete_euro_dark_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, company_name AS cn, company_type AS ct, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind in ('cast','crew','complete+verified') AND (cn.name like '%Amblin Partners%' OR cn.name like '%Sony Pictures Entertainment%' OR cn.name like '%Miramax%' OR cn.name like '%Focus Features%') AND it2.info in ('copyright holder','LD language','book','where now','nick names','LD picture format','weekend gross','quotes','other literature','LD release date','magazine cover photo','certificates','LD release country','LD certification','taglines','genres','LD disc format','soundtrack','sound mix','LD label') AND kt.kind not in ('movie','episode','video game','tv series')
